<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{سَلام عَلَيْكُم}</span> وَهَذِهِ تَحِيَّةُ أَهْلِ الْجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ محمدٌ:</span> الْمَعْنَى: يَقُولُونَ: سلامٌ عَلَيْكُمْ؛ فَأُضْمِرَ الْقَوْلُ؛ إِذْ فِي الْكَلامِ مَا يَدُلُّ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{بِمَا صَبَرْتُمْ}</span> فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سُورَة الرَّعْد من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>